%F A053984 a(n) = Sum_{k = 0..floor((n-1)/2)} (-1)^k*2^(n-2*k-1)*(n-2*k-1)!*binomial(n-k-1,k)*binomial(n-k-1/2,k+1/2), cf. A058798. - _Peter Bala_, Aug 01 2013
