%F A053984 0 = a(n)*(+a(n+2)) + a(n+1)*(-a(n+1) + 2*a(n+2) - a(n+3)) + a(n+2)*(+a(n+2)) for all n in Z. - _Michael Somos_, Sep 11 2014
